<div type="definition">
<p>SPEAK so as to PLAY INTENDING thereby to CAUSE OTHERS to LAUGH.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The most current general word is perhaps xì 戲 "be less than serious". 戲耳　"I was just joking".</p>
<p>2. Xié 諧 refers to playfulness in the making up of stories.</p></div>
